body_html:
Try to do an ls -l ~/graphs/inception/tensorflow_inception_graph.pb to see if the file is indeed there.

If so and the error still persists, try to expand "~" to the absolute path when launching the program.

Feel free to reopen if there's still issues.

body:
Try to do an `ls -l  ~/graphs/inception/tensorflow_inception_graph.pb` to see if the file is indeed there.

If so and the error still persists, try to expand "~" to the absolute path when launching the program.

Feel free to reopen if there's still issues.
